或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d9aede8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=05209449\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf</a><br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d6b65e61\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=73e54af0\" target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">交表</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=2b2ad2f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">免費傳真方法 </span></strong><br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=a6f273d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]2019選民登記 推爆佢 7月2號截止<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]"},{"pid":"08fbbc2a59732ecc013008fd26c6fa8456a1f1ea","tid":1269862,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5b6fdae9f05813a5622ce40c2461f3579edb5535","tid":1269862,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:52:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7343f3fa5182adeedb2fda2c6fe73b7a8ceebdb9","tid":1269862,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7300695f178e957276aa9f8ea76cf7b137ddf025","tid":1269862,"uid":262428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbfl-campaign.github.io%2F&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d5fef992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/</a> &lt;&lt; 網上填表工具<br />\n後日就截止申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\